reviewText: Austin really love s the power rangers and watches it all the time.  he really enjoys it, he watches it at bedtime.

Power Rangers Wild Force was simply not good enough as a series, especially as the next series to follow Power Rangers Time Force.
The episodes on this video are barely average and the ending isn't particularly conclusive. Unlike previous Power Rangers videos, this one ends on a cliffhanger, and it isn't very welcome because the resolution isn't even available on video.

The Rangers find out that Zen-Aku is really Merick one of the six ancient warriors who protected Animeria, the rangers manage to free Merick; later Merick becomes the Lunar Wolf Ranger the sixth Wild Force Ranger with these power he joins the Rangers to defeate Master Org.
